Sysadmin tools - Delegated User Creation

    make-user.sh  

  A simple user creation script for delegated administrators.
  Allows non-experts to add users to a Linux server. 
  Useful when many new users are expected to be added over time.


    HOWTO-MakeUser.pdf

  Instruction sheet for delegated admin.


    disk_usage_report.pl

  Generates a report of disk usage with min/max/avg. 


  
